Test (F /dev/dvb/adapter1/frontend0) + I AddToMenu /Playlist-button '$[gt.Channels] DVB 2' PopUp /Music/ChannelSet2
Test (F /dev/dvb/adapter2/frontend0) + I AddToMenu /Playlist-button '$[gt.Watch DVB] 3' Music-WatchDVB 3
